static inline struct timeval ktime_to_timeval(const ktime_t kt)
{
	return (struct timeval) {
		.tv_sec = (time_t) kt.tv.sec,
		.tv_usec = (suseconds_t) (kt.tv.nsec / NSEC_PER_USEC) };
